    "body" : "<p>See the javadoc </p>\n\n<p>of <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/1.5.0/docs/api/java/util/List.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">List</a></p>\n\n<pre><code>list.get(0);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/1.5.0/docs/api/java/util/Set.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Set</a></p>\n\n<pre><code>set.iterator().next();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>and check the size before using the above methods by invoking <code>isEmpty()</code></p>\n\n<pre><code>!list_or_set.isEmpty()\n</code></pre>\n"
