    "answer_id" : 43324775,
    "question_id" : 8882295,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I'm surprised that nobody suggested guava solution yet:</p>\n\n<pre><code>com.google.common.collect.Iterables.get(collection, 0)\n// or\ncom.google.common.collect.Iterables.get(collection, 0, defaultValue)\n// or\ncom.google.common.collect.Iterables.getFirst(collection, defaultValue)\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or if you expect single element:</p>\n\n<pre><code>com.google.common.collect.Iterables.getOnlyElement(collection, defaultValue)\n// or\ncom.google.common.collect.Iterables.getOnlyElement(collection)\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
