      "body" : "@pavan this is because according to the documentation, the <code>findFirst()</code> &quot;Returns an Optional describing the first element of this stream, or an empty Optional if the stream is empty. &quot;. I&#39;ve also mentioned twice &quot;Followed by or encapsulated within the appropriate checks or try-catch blocks&quot; so it really depends on your case"
